Edward Farley (born 17 October 1987) is a former international cricketer who played for Jersey.
Farley was educated at Eton College and Durham University. In 2014 he played in the 2014 ICC World Cricket League Division Four tournament, and was selected in the Jersey squad for the 2015 ICC World Twenty20 Qualifier tournament.
